{"tid":2097002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"熱血公民鄭錦滿：今年唔想再用 #港島唯一本土派 呢個tag，我哋係「本土自由派」。","createTime":"2020-07-06T13:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-06T14:28:51.000Z","uid":271829,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"eab472312747d146b8827b9378bab54fe79de2b5","tid":2097002,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:35:05.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿：<br />\n今日銅鑼灣東角道街站，有位熱狗帶一位女士禮貌地問我問題。<br />\n女士：「點解初選論壇唔見你哋嘅？」<br />\n我：「因為所謂『泛民初選』係篩選，我哋拒絕參與小圈子篩選。」<br />\n然後我再解釋一大輪到底咩係「初選」、民主原則、比例代表制等等嘅問題。<br />\n直至最後，該位女士問：「咁我都想知你哋同泛民有咩分別。」<br />\n我：「我哋追求民主、自由，拒絕小圈子篩選。」<br />\n及後，有位年輕人主動走過來問係咪可以簽名提名我哋，表示所有參與泛民初選嘅都唔係本土派，只投不蛇鼠一窩嘅本土派。<br />\n今年唔想再用 #港島唯一本土派 呢個tag，我哋係「本土自由派」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgExbF6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgExbF6.png&h=9b97a4ab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"def4ea1b7507dd5152026ccec49ae9ab6908b6a4","tid":2097002,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n國安法47條已經打到黎<br />\n理呢D撚樣做乜春"},{"pid":"09be59b712b81fc5e2ae80680e7a496192d18a82","tid":2097002,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"def4ea1b7507dd5152026ccec49ae9ab6908b6a4","tid":2097002,"uid":154486,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:36:53.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n國安法47條已經打到黎<br />\n理呢D撚樣做乜春"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OqGteq.png&amp;h=c9948207&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"8143885783c66fb7a4dae2355e5b232305c1b11d","tid":2097002,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:42:35.000Z","msg":"本土熱血狗派"},{"pid":"2c55ac686d7cfbc9979f5a97d63a9aa52e15b76a","tid":2097002,"uid":316927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:43:48.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"81d4cdcb308219ad2d63a78d075e7272029975a4","tid":2097002,"uid":44038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一票不投熱狗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9181ae726707c9ab6a1a953634d1fb270250540b","tid":2097002,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T13:54:45.000Z","msg":"戇鳩唔想理"},{"pid":"ac696889f8019d810b1ddc663b4e6f3afb89c66b","tid":2097002,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T14:28:51.000Z","msg":"四眼練好把口未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}